description: '### New functions for testing framework\n\nThere are new functions for
  doing mutation testing directly from files, that originate a mutated version of
  the contract and then gives control to the passed function that can do the test:\n-
  `Test.originate_from_file_and_mutate : string -> string -> string list -> michelson_program
  -> tez -> (address auto_merge_request.sh release_metadata retrieve_merge_request_info.sh
  update_distribution_references_with_release.sh versioning_website.sh michelson_contract
  auto_merge_request.sh release_metadata retrieve_merge_request_info.sh update_distribution_references_with_release.sh
  versioning_website.sh int -> b) -> (b auto_merge_request.sh release_metadata retrieve_merge_request_info.sh
  update_distribution_references_with_release.sh versioning_website.sh mutation) option`\n-
  `Test.originate_from_file_and_mutate_all : string -> string -> string list -> michelson_program
  -> tez -> (address auto_merge_request.sh release_metadata retrieve_merge_request_info.sh
  update_distribution_references_with_release.sh versioning_website.sh michelson_contract
  auto_merge_request.sh release_metadata retrieve_merge_request_info.sh update_distribution_references_with_release.sh
  versioning_website.sh int -> b) -> (b auto_merge_request.sh release_metadata retrieve_merge_request_info.sh
  update_distribution_references_with_release.sh versioning_website.sh mutation) list`'
